casebody.head_matter:
UNITED STATES, petitioner,
v.
Jason Daniel SIMS.
No. 17-766.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 23, 2018.
Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit granted. The case is consolidated and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
